# Voxel world

- Streaming: `ChunkStreamingSystem` — horizontal slice, Y locked to `stream_y_chunk=0`, X/Z hysteresis.
- Mesh budget: `mesh_chunks_per_frame` in config — do not mesh all dirty chunks in one frame.
- Collision: `VoxelCollisionSystem` after player movement; uses `world_query.py`.
- Cross-chunk seams: meshgen needs neighbor chunk data (known gap).
- Tests: `tests/world/`, `tests/voxel/`, `tests/test_chunk_streaming.py`, `tests/test_performance.py`.
